# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok u.s. olympic committee chief executive lloyd ward says he did nothing wrong in trying to steer olympic business to a company with ties to his brother .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Lloyd"
                  :op2 "Ward")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (o / organization
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Olympic"
                              :op2 "Committee"))
                  :ARG2 (e / executive
                        :mod (c / chief))))
      :ARG1 (w / wrong-02
            :ARG1 p
            :ARG2 (t / try-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (s2 / steer-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (b / business
                              :mod o)
                        :ARG2 (c2 / company
                              :ARG1-of (t2 / tie-01
                                    :ARG2 (p2 / person
                                          :ARG0-of (h2 / have-rel-role-91
                                                :ARG1 p
                                                :ARG2 (b2 / brother)))))))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok morison s. cousins , a designer who brought flashy , <unk> designs to tupperware without sacrificing its polyethylene american soul , died on feb. ## in orlando , fla. .
# ::alignments
(d / die-01
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-rel-role-91
                  :ARG1 (p2 / person
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Morison"))
                  :ARG2 (c / cousin))
            :ARG0-of (b / bring-01
                  :ARG1 (d2 / design-01
                        :ARG1-of (f / flash-02))
                  :ARG2 (p3 / product
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Tupperware"))
                  :manner (s / sacrifice-01
                        :polarity -
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (s2 / soul
                              :mod (c2 / country
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "America"))
                              :mod (p4 / polyethylene)
                              :poss p3))))
      :time (f2 / festival
            :name (n4 / name
                  :op1 "Feb."))
      :location (c3 / city
            :name (n5 / name
                  :op1 "Orlando")))

                  :ARG1 c

            :polarity -
            :op1 (p / password)
            :op2 (h3 / handshake
                  :mod (s / secret))))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                        :mod (w / war-01)
                        :ARG1-of (b / bulge-01)
                        :mod (c4 / campaign-01))))
      :ARG2 (r / run-04
            :ARG1 (t / time)
            :ARG2 (s2 / short-06
                  :ARG1 t
                  :ARG2 (c5 / catch-02
                        :ARG0 (p2 / person
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Barack"
                                    :op2 "Obama"))
                        :ARG1 (p3 / person
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Clinton")
                              :ARG0-of (r2 / rival-01
                                    :ARG1 (p4 / political-party
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "White"
                                                :op2 "House")))
                              :mod (h3 / hillary))))))
